videos.description: Oregon's Sabrina Ionescu comes up with a steal on defense and takes it the other way for an easy transition layup.

videos.description: Oregon's Sabrina Ionescu's shot from deep bounces off the rim, off the top of the backboard, then twice more on the rim to get the fortuitous roll for 3.
